summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to land use and zoning; amending Plat 36E, Page 103 of the official Land Use Map to rezone certain property in Block 47 of Nagle's Addition to the City of Seattle from Midrise (MR) to Midrise/Residental Commercial (MR/RC) Zone (Petition of Larry Heath, C.F. 295541), and superseding Ordinance 114149.
